{"view":"article","slug":"top-white-separated-f2l","category":"3x3","subcategory":null,"topDir":"3x3","title":{"en":"Top White, Separated F2L Algorithms","zh":"白顶分离F2L公式"},"content":{"en":"<p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/top-white-separated-f2l/en/image2.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/top-white-separated-f2l/en/image4.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/top-white-separated-f2l/en/image6.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/top-white-separated-f2l/en/image8.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong>Top White, Separated F2L Algorithms</strong></p><p>This article gives the method to determine whether the top white, separated <a href=\"/tutorial/f2l\" class=\"see-also-link\" data-see-also=\"true\">F2L</a> starts with R U* R' or R' U* R. Ignore all non-target slots and assume that \"slot\" refers to target slot. First move edge to UL/UR position. First move.</p><p><strong>Method 1: CE Recognition (Corner and Edge)</strong></p><p>Scramble. Recognize the top sticker of edge, and the corner sticker in one of positions below: </p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/top-white-separated-f2l/en/image10.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"4\"><p><strong>Matched Color</strong></p><p>Start with R/L'.</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/top-white-separated-f2l/en/image12.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/top-white-separated-f2l/en/image8.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/top-white-separated-f2l/en/image14.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/top-white-separated-f2l/en/image16.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/top-white-separated-f2l/en/image18.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/top-white-separated-f2l/en/image20.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/top-white-separated-f2l/en/image22.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/top-white-separated-f2l/en/image24.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>R U2' R'-&gt;pair</strong></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R U R' U' R U2 R'\">R U R' U' R U2 R'</span></p></td><td><p><strong>R U R'-&gt;pair</strong></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R U R' U' R U' R'\">R U R' U' R U' R'</span></p></td><td><p><strong>L' U2 L-&gt;pair</strong></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"L' U' L U L' U2 L\">L' U' L U L' U2 L</span></p></td><td><p><strong>L' U' L-&gt;pair</strong></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"L' U' L U L' U L\">L' U' L U L' U L</span></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"4\"></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"4\"><p><strong>Adjacent Color</strong></p><p>Start with R'/L.</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/top-white-separated-f2l/en/image26.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/top-white-separated-f2l/en/image6.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/top-white-separated-f2l/en/image28.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/top-white-separated-f2l/en/image30.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/top-white-separated-f2l/en/image32.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/top-white-separated-f2l/en/image34.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/top-white-separated-f2l/en/image36.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/top-white-separated-f2l/en/image38.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>R' U' R-&gt;pair</strong></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"F' U' F R' U R\">F' U' F R' U R</span></p></td><td><p><strong>R' U2' R-&gt;pair</strong></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"F' U' F R' U2' R\">F' U' F R' U2' R</span></p></td><td><p><strong>L U L'-&gt;pair</strong></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"F U F' L U' L'\">F U F' L U' L'</span></p></td><td><p><strong>L U2' L'-&gt;pair</strong></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"F U F' L U2 L'\">F U F' L U2 L'</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>Method 2: EX Recognition (Edge and Center)</strong></p><p>L/R-mirrors are excluded. Recognize the side sticker of edge, and the center attached to the edge. Slot.</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"2\"><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/top-white-separated-f2l/en/image40.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><strong>Aligned Case</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"4\"><p>Start with R* which moves edge away from slot.</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/top-white-separated-f2l/en/image42.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/top-white-separated-f2l/en/image44.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/top-white-separated-f2l/en/image46.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/top-white-separated-f2l/en/image48.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R U2' R' U R U' R'\">R U2' R' U R U' R'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R U R' U R U' R'\">R U R' U R U' R'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R' U' R U' R' U R\">R' U' R U' R' U R</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R' U2' R U' R' U R\">R' U2' R U' R' U R</span></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"4\"></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\"><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/top-white-separated-f2l/en/image50.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><strong>Checker Case</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"4\"><p>Start with R* which moves close to slot.</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/top-white-separated-f2l/en/image52.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/top-white-separated-f2l/en/image54.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/top-white-separated-f2l/en/image56.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/top-white-separated-f2l/en/image58.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R U2' R' f R' f'\">R U2' R' f R' f'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R U R' f R' f'\">R U R' f R' f'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R' U' R y L' U L\">R' U' R y L' U L</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R' U2' R y L' U L\">R' U2' R y L' U L</span></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"4\"></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\"><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/top-white-separated-f2l/en/image60.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><strong>Opposite Case</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"4\"><p>Start with R* which moves close to slot, i.e., moves edge to the center whose color matches the top sticker of edge.</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/top-white-separated-f2l/en/image62.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/top-white-separated-f2l/en/image64.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/top-white-separated-f2l/en/image66.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/top-white-separated-f2l/en/image68.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R U2' R' L U2 L'\">R U2' R' L U2 L'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R U R' L U2 L'\">R U R' L U2 L'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R' U' R L' U2 L\">R' U' R L' U2 L</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R' U2' R L' U2 L\">R' U2' R L' U2 L</span></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"4\"></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\"><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/top-white-separated-f2l/en/image70.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><strong>Misaligned Case</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"4\"><p>Do d move into aligned case; or start with R* which moves edge away from slot (not recommended).</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/top-white-separated-f2l/en/image72.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/top-white-separated-f2l/en/image74.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/top-white-separated-f2l/en/image76.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/top-white-separated-f2l/en/image78.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"d R U2' R' U R U' R'\">d R U2' R' U R U' R'</span></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R U2' R' U2 F U' F'\">R U2' R' U2 F U' F'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"d R U R' U R U' R'\">d R U R' U R U' R'</span></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R U R' U2 F U' F'\">R U R' U2 F U' F'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"d' R' U' R U' R' U R\">d' R' U' R U' R' U R</span></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R' U' R U2 y R' U R\">R' U' R U2 y R' U R</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"d' R' U2' R U' R' U R\">d' R' U2' R U' R' U R</span></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R' U2' R U2 y R' U R\">R' U2' R U2 y R' U R</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div>","zh":"<p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/top-white-separated-f2l/zh/image2.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/top-white-separated-f2l/zh/image4.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/top-white-separated-f2l/zh/image6.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/top-white-separated-f2l/zh/image8.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong>白顶分离F2L公式</strong></p><p>本文给出了判断白顶分离<a href=\"/tutorial/f2l\" class=\"see-also-link\" data-see-also=\"true\">F2L</a>公式开头是R U* R'还是R' U* R的方法. 忽略所有非目标槽并假设\"槽\"指目标槽. 先将棱移至UL/UR位置. 第一步.</p><p><strong>方法1: 观察棱和角</strong></p><p>打乱. 观察棱的顶面格, 和处于以下位置之一的角格:</p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/top-white-separated-f2l/zh/image10.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"4\"><p><strong>同色</strong></p><p>先做R/L'.</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/top-white-separated-f2l/zh/image12.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/top-white-separated-f2l/zh/image8.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/top-white-separated-f2l/zh/image14.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/top-white-separated-f2l/zh/image16.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/top-white-separated-f2l/zh/image18.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/top-white-separated-f2l/zh/image20.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/top-white-separated-f2l/zh/image22.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/top-white-separated-f2l/zh/image24.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>R U2' R'-&gt;组对</strong></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R U R' U' R U2 R'\">R U R' U' R U2 R'</span></p></td><td><p><strong>R U R'-&gt;组对</strong></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R U R' U' R U' R'\">R U R' U' R U' R'</span></p></td><td><p><strong>L' U2 L-&gt;组对</strong></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"L' U' L U L' U2 L\">L' U' L U L' U2 L</span></p></td><td><p><strong>L' U' L-&gt;组对</strong></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"L' U' L U L' U L\">L' U' L U L' U L</span></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"4\"></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"4\"><p><strong>邻色</strong></p><p>先做R'/L.</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/top-white-separated-f2l/zh/image26.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/top-white-separated-f2l/zh/image6.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/top-white-separated-f2l/zh/image28.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/top-white-separated-f2l/zh/image30.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/top-white-separated-f2l/zh/image32.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/top-white-separated-f2l/zh/image34.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/top-white-separated-f2l/zh/image36.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/top-white-separated-f2l/zh/image38.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>R' U' R-&gt;组对</strong></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"F' U' F R' U R\">F' U' F R' U R</span></p></td><td><p><strong>R' U2' R-&gt;组对</strong></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"F' U' F R' U2' R\">F' U' F R' U2' R</span></p></td><td><p><strong>L U L'-&gt;组对</strong></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"F U F' L U' L'\">F U F' L U' L'</span></p></td><td><p><strong>L U2' L'-&gt;组对</strong></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"F U F' L U2 L'\">F U F' L U2 L'</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>方法2: 观察棱和心</strong></p><p>不包括左右镜像. 槽. 观察棱的侧面格和紧挨棱的心.</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"2\"><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/top-white-separated-f2l/zh/image40.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><strong>对齐情况</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"4\"><p>先做R*使棱远离槽位.</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/top-white-separated-f2l/zh/image42.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/top-white-separated-f2l/zh/image44.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/top-white-separated-f2l/zh/image46.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/top-white-separated-f2l/zh/image48.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R U2' R' U R U' R'\">R U2' R' U R U' R'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R U R' U R U' R'\">R U R' U R U' R'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R' U' R U' R' U R\">R' U' R U' R' U R</span></p></td